        "timestamp": "2021-07-06 21:23:35.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI also saw references to \"schema\", which appears to be extracted from the directory or file name.  However, I don't see a schema in any of the names.\n\ncan probably remove \"policy-jdk\" directory component (i.e., move src/main up one level)",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
