        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2021-07-07 00:19:10.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2:\n> \n> I also saw references to \"schema\", which appears to be extracted from the directory or file name.  However, I don't see a schema in any of the names.\n> \n> can probably remove \"policy-jdk\" directory component (i.e., move src/main up one level)\n\nschema is a synonymous to database for this tool (see the comment section in the file may be useful for details).   The tool assumed the following dir structure:   <database>/sql/<scripts>.",
